name: Plant Virual walkthrough Interactive for the Oculus Rift S
name_original: Plant Virual walkthrough Interactive for the Oculus Rift S
description:
A plant Interactive experience designed for the Oculus Rift S. Walk past the big crane and it will start a crane lift scenario. Open and close valves, pick up items along the way.

Take a walk through my interactive world for a nice view!
